snippet.title: London Fields (2018) Amber Heard, Johnny Depp, Crime, Mystery, Thriller Movie - Trailer #1 [HD]
snippet.description:
HOT New Trailers: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcUYOz0HwvHFo09XxdHzv_VG_TdRt5bvs


Clairvoyant femme fatale Nicola Six has been living with a dark premonition of her impending death by murder. She begins a tangled love affair with three uniquely different men: one of whom she knows will be her murderer.
Director: Mathew Cullen
Writers: Martin Amis (novel), Roberta Hanley
Stars: Amber Heard, Gemma Chan, Cara Delevingne
